   "translate": "The Weapon Forms"
  },
  "subtitle": {
   "text": "Simply Swords adds 15 weapon forms. Each one fights differently."
  },
  "description": [
   "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
   "  CH.03 · THE WEAPON FORMS",
   "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
   "",
   "▸ Simply Swords adds 15 weapon archetypes.",
   "  Each crafted from standard materials.",
   "  Each with different attack patterns, reach, and speed.",
   "",
   "◈ THE 15 WEAPON TYPES",
   "  └ ⚔ Greatsword — slow, high damage, wide sweep",
   "  └ ⚔ Rapier — fast, piercing, low knockback",
   "  └ ⚔ Katana — medium speed, bonus crit chance",
   "  └ ⚔ Saber — cavalry bonus, mounted damage",
   "  └ ⚔ Claymore — Scottish two-hander, reach",
   "  └ ⚔ Longsword — balanced, all-purpose",
   "  └ ⚔ Twinblade — dual-tip, combo attacks",
   "  └ ⚔ Warhammer — blunt, armor penetration",
   "  └ ⚔ Spear — extended reach, throw ability",
   "  └ ⚔ Halberd — pole-axe, sweep + thrust",
   "  └ ⚔ Scythe — harvest weapon, wide arc",
   "  └ ⚔ Dagger — small, fast, backstab bonus",
   "  └ ⚔ Quarterstaff — reach, no sharp damage",
   "  └ ⚔ Battle Axe — cleave through armor",
   "  └ ⚔ Falchion — curved blade, fast swings",
   "",
   "◈ GEM SYSTEM",
   "  └ Weapons can have gem slots",
   "  └ Socket gems for stat bonuses",
   "  └ Gems found in dungeon loot, boss drops",
   "  └ Multiple gem slots on high-tier weapons",
   "",
   "◈ SCROLL: The Weapon Forms",
   "  └ Found in: blacksmith chests, combat school ruins,",
   "    armory loot, warrior graves",
   "  └ Research time: 20 min",
   "  └ Unlocks: all 15 weapon type awareness, gem socket knowledge",
   "",
   "▸ The scroll is worn smooth at the edges.",
   "  Someone read it until the paper thinned.",
   "  Then they picked a form and practiced until they didn't need it.",
   "",
   "▶ Find The Weapon Forms scroll [check]",
   "▶ Craft any Simply Swords specialty weapon [check]",
   "",
   "◇ On The Blade scroll (this chain, next) covers",
   "  the combat philosophy behind weapon choice.",
   "  Read both before Ch11."
  ],
